title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/Mileski/Russo/Ramsey/Leber/Hebert
description: #92Noon is back in the Xcel Energy Center penalty box! Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau stops by to talk with PA, Brandon Mileski co-hosts the first hour, The Athletic's Michael Russo shares his thoughts on the Wild, Ben Leber joins the show to talk football, Rachel Ramsey talks all things puck including the Minnesota Whitecaps, and Bobby Hebert shares his thoughts on the Saints-Vikings Sunday NIght Footbal battle this weekend!
